reviewText: Good price for a very good music CD. The songs are inspiring and uplifting.
loved Dwayne's song "Flowers" especially when he sung to his grandmother and mother
I order this cd for my 75 year old grandpa he was thrilled. I was so happy to see a smile on his face!
can not hear all of the 1st song on the dvd, the remaining is great.
An excellent concert to watch during my leisure time as well as when I entertain guest(s) in my home.

I can guarantee that if you love the Canton Spirituals as much as I do, that you will love this DVD as well.  I first listened to this group when I was about 12 years old.  I fell completely in love with their style of music. Like my favorite, Dwayne Watkins, I too was changed at the age of 10.  So, "Cool Change"  really touched my heart.  I just love all the music on this DVD and I believe you will too if you are true Canton Spirituals fan like I am.  This DVD, will have you "Smoothin" up the rough way with new home up on high.  Therefore I give it all the stars in Heaven!!!
Very uplifting spiritual songs. I'm glad I ordered this dvd. It's truly a blessing for me and my family. It's very enjoyable.

This DVD was purchased for my mother as part of her mothers day gifts need less to say it was a Hugh hit a really big home run it offers a great form of entertainment for any one that love great gospel music
This is an uplifting DVD. The Canton Spirituals are interesting, personal, and enjoy leading those in attendance in worship and praise.
I always feel blessed when I listen to the Canton Spirituals! Wonderful and annointed they are! May they continue to keep singing and lifting up the Lord through their music!
I have been playing it over and over again.  I would like to order the cd soon, so I can listen to it while driving.  I love it

I'm a old school quartet person that really love this type of music, and I feel that everyone in the entire world should purchase this DVD. The Canton Spirituals are an amazing quartet group that will keep you on your feet with their great music. " I'm glad that I got Jesus" takes you close to being in heaven, wow what a song. Everything about this DVD such as sound, lights, and the group energy is superb .
This has to be the concert of concerts.  Had me on my feet the whole time! Yes, who says men aren't sensitive!  Tears of JOY in my eyes!  Must see again!

I enjoyed this dvd just as much as the other 2 that I purchased. I'm waiting to purchase my third one as soon as it comes out on DVD "Live in Memphis 2" it is really awesome I have it on vhs, but I need it on DVD.
Great DVD! Great condition and prompt delivery! Whole family enjoys it! They're in touch with how gospel music is supposed to be!
I have this dvd and it is very good, the songs are very good it will but you in a good mood. A must have

You have to purchase this dvd, if you don't you will be very sorry. This is one of the best groups in gospel music today their music reaches not only the black audiences but different audiences world wide. I promise you won't be sorry that you did.

hello from chicago, i give this copy of a gift to a rather wonderful spiritual person. she played it over and over till i bought her another one she said, the other one was losing its quality.. she enjoys it so much. by the way the person i give it to was my boss...

The Canton are and will always be my favorite gospel group. I pray and hope they will find their way to San Diego or Los Angeles, CA. I would be the first in line to purchase a ticket. Whenever I am at my lowest, I  listen to their music and get filled with the holy spirit and I  can then  conquer another day and know that god is by my side. Their voices are truly  an inspiration and I can feel it deep within my soul. May God continue to  bless them and keep them. I have all their Video tapes and as soon as a new  one comes out, I rush out to buy it.
